Privacy Policy for ProductTrace App

Effective Date: 19th November, 2023

Thank you for using ProductTrace, an app developed by ShaheenDevs. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application.

Information We Collect:

ProductTrace does not collect any personal information or data from its users. The app operates without requiring users to log in or sign up, and it does not store any personal details.

Barcode Scanning:

ProductTrace allows users to scan barcodes to retrieve information about a product. The app does not store the scanned barcode information or associate it with any user account. The barcode data is processed locally within the app, and no data is transmitted or stored externally.

Location Information:

ProductTrace does not access or track your location. The app does not request or utilize location services on your device.

Cookies and Tracking:

ProductTrace does not use cookies or any tracking mechanisms to collect information about users' activities.

Third-Party Services:

ProductTrace does not integrate with any third-party services for The app operates independently without sharing user data with external parties.

Data Security:

We take the security of your information seriously. ProductTrace employs industry-standard security measures to protect against unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction of data.

Children's Privacy:

ProductTrace is not designed for use by individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect or solicit personal information from children. If a parent or guardian becomes aware that their child has provided us with personal information, please contact us, and we will promptly delete such information from our records.

Changes to This Privacy Policy:

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page, and the effective date will be updated accordingly.

Contact Us:

If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy or the use of ProductTrace, please contact us at mudassirmukhtar4@gmail.com.

By using ProductTrace, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.

